==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Atomic bomb
<hw>A*tom"ic bomb`</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>a bomb of great power in which the explosive energy is derived from
the nuclear fission of a fissionable material, such as plutonium or
uranium-235. It is a type of <hypen>nuclear weapon</hypen>. The strength
of an atom bomb is measured in <it>kilotons</it>, i.e. the equivalent
energy released by explosion of a thousand tons of TNT. The first atomic
bomb was manufactured in 1945.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> A-bomb, fission bomb.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

